<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَالدُّعَاءُ لَهُ بَعْدَ الدَّفْنِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> وَرَشُّ القَبْرِ بِمَاءٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> وَرَفْعُهُ قَدْرَ شِبْرٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ مَاتَتْ حَامِلٌ:</span> حَرُمَ شَقُّ بَطْنِهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَأَخْرَجَ النِّسَاءُ مَنْ تُرْجَى حَيَاتُهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَإِنْ تَعَذَّرَ:</span> لَمْ تُدْفَنْ حَتَّى يَمُوتَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ خَرَجَ بَعْضُهُ حَيًّا:</span> شُقَّ لِلْبَاقِي.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَلَوْ مَاتَ قَبْلَ الشَّقِّ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- أُخْرِجَ حَتَّى يُغَسَّلَ وَيُكَفَّنَ بِلَا شَقٍّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَإِنْ تَعَذَّرَ إِخْرَاجُهُ غُسِلَ مَا خَرَجَ مِنْهُ وَصُلِّيَ عَلَيْهِ مَعَهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ أَرْبَعَةُ أَشْهَرٍ فَأَكْثَرُ:</span> صُلِّيَ عَلَيْهَا دُونَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَتَعْزِيَةُ مُسْلِمٍ -وَلَوْ صَغِيرًا-<span style="color:#006d98"> إِلَى ثَلَاثَةِ أَيَّامٍ:</span> سُنَّةٌ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَيُقَالُ لِمُسْلِمٍ مُصَابٍ بِمُسْلِمٍ:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(أَعْظَمَ اللهُ أَجْرَكَ، وَأَحْسَنَ عَزَاءَكَ، وَغَفَرَ لِمَيْتِكَ)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>